  <user-story>
    <as-a>buyer or maker</as-a>
    <i-want>to resolve shipping issues (lost packages</i-want>
    <so-that>transactions can be completed fairly for both parties</so-that>
  </user-story>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion id="ac1">**BUSINESS CRITICAL**: Buyer can report issues (not received, damaged, wrong item, quality issue) with evidence upload and detailed description within 14 days of delivery date.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac2">Maker can respond to issues within 48 hours with counter-evidence, resolution offers (refund, replacement, partial refund), and explanation of circumstances.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac3">**BUSINESS CRITICAL**: Platform can mediate disputes with refund/replacement options, payment hold/release authority, and final binding decisions when parties cannot agree.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac4">Insurance claims can be filed for high-value items (&gt;$500) lost or damaged in transit with carrier claims integration and documentation support.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac5">**BUSINESS CRITICAL**: Resolution timeline is enforced (5 business days max) with automated escalation to support team and SLA breach alerts for unresolved cases.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac6">Maker rating is protected for legitimate shipping issues beyond their control (carrier delays, lost packages, damage in transit) with neutral feedback flagging.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
